<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <title>리뷰상세</title>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.3.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</head>

<!-- id 속성 => 고유한 식별을 목적으로 하는 경우 사용
                 class 속성 => 재사용을 목적으로 하는 경우 사용
                 name 속성 => form 컨트롤 요소의 값(value)을 서버로 전송하기 위해 필요한 속성 -->

<body>

    <div class="container">
        <h2>리뷰상세보기</h2>
        <p></p>
        <form method="POST">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="user_id">유저 아이디:</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="user_id" name="user_id" value="<%= data.user_id%>" disabled>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="grade">평점:</label>
                <input type="number" class="form-control" id="grade" name="grade" value="<%= data.grade%>" disabled>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="contents">내용:</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="contents" name="contents" value="<%= data.contents%>" disabled>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="univ_id">대학이름:</label>
                <input type="number" class="form-control" id="univ_id" name="univ_id" value="<%= data.univ_id%>" disabled>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="depart_name">학과이름:</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="depart_name" name="depart_name" value="<%= data.depart_name%>" disabled>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>

</body>

</html>